_:Nd3b5fbe8228e4f09b474537c6ee88517 <http://schema.org/text> "Government Tax profession is one of the largest Civil Service Professions with approximately 17,000 tax professionals working across government in the UK. " <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
_:Nd3b5fbe8228e4f09b474537c6ee88517 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/Article> <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
